# OKF knowledge edits

When editing files under `knowledge/`:

- Concepts are document packages: `<slug>/<title-slug>.md` + `convert.yaml`.
- Concept source `.md` files (not `index.md` / `log.md`) must keep YAML frontmatter with a non-empty `type`.
- Prefer recommended fields: `title`, `description`, `tags`, `timestamp`.
- Use bundle-relative absolute links: `[Title](/category/slug/<title-slug>.md)`.
- Update category + root `knowledge/index.md` when adding or renaming concepts.
- Add a newest-first entry to `knowledge/log.md` for meaningful structural changes.
- After bulk edits, run `pnpm okf:check`.
